    "uen": "200605471Z",
    "description": "<p>This is where Blue Star System plays a role in your organization’s operational plans. Blue Star System’s core competence is in the repair, servicing, maintenance and inventory of parts to ensure that your assets function optimally. We are more than mere providers of services that make operational continuity in the short term possible; we are your strategic partner with an extended long term view to ensure effective preservation of your asset’s useful life.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>In today’s demanding globalised economy, businesses strive towards achieving optimal performance at the lowest cost possible without sacrificing quality. The world’s leading companies are seeking innovative ways to improve operational efficiencies, mostly by simultaneously pushing operational production output and extending capital asset lives to achieve potential economic benefits. As a result, curtailing expenditure on capital equipment has rendered good maintenance practices to become an even more important key success factor.</p>",
